'''天主教伊帕梅里教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Ipameriensis}}；{{lang-pt|Diocese de Ipameri}}）是[[巴西|巴西]]一個[[天主教|天主教]][[教區|教區]]，位於[[戈亞斯州|戈亞斯州]]東南部，屬[[天主教戈亞尼亞總教區|戈亞尼亞總教區]]。

教區成立於1966年10月11日。<ref>{{cite web |title=GOIANIENSIS ET ALIARUM (ANNAPOLITANAE - IPAMERIENSIS - ITUMBIARENSIS MIRACEMANAE SUPERIORIS - RUBIATABENSIS) |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/paul-vi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_p-vi_apc_19661011_goianiensis.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2019-08-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811202356/https://w2.vatican.va/content/paul-vi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_p-vi_apc_19661011_goianiensis.html |archivedate=2019-08-11 |language=la |date=1966-10-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2006年有教友214,000人，佔總人口75.1%。有十五個堂區、司鐸十七人。現任教區主教為{{link-pt|若瑟·方濟各·羅德里格斯-多-雷戈|José Francisco Rodrigues do Rêgo}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 15.05.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/05/15/190515b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-08-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811171811/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/05/15/190515b.html |archivedate=2019-08-11 |language=en |date=2019-05-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

